{"tid":1412264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血義診 中醫 物治 西醫 心理輔導 推比有需要既巴打們","createTime":"2019-08-05T05:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T00:20:53.000Z","uid":107060,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"befc78de7c26145aeacfb972e1acdfd14d3f2bcd","tid":1412264,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:59:43.000Z","msg":"#熱血義診<br />\n<br />\n由7月底起，特別是國務院記招正式宣告香港進入「警察政府」後，警方使用的暴力及武器鎮壓越趨嚴重，有示威者接連吸入催淚煙患上呼吸道問題，甚至有議員表示肺部感到不適。<br />\n<br />\n有一些熱心醫護人員聯絡本人，希望可以提供義務醫療協助，分別有：<br />\n<br />\n1. 中醫診治（中醫師特別強調，累積吸入催淚煙，需要中醫調理幫助排毒，從中醫角度，這才能治本，不用登記及記錄）<br />\n<br />\n2. 物理治療（物理治療師表示，受傷的義士（主要是關節受傷）可以尋求協助，亦備有便攜的治療器材可供外展使用；主治筋骨傷、甩骱、撞傷，識做都做，不用登記及記錄）<br />\n<br />\n3. 西醫門診<br />\n<br />\n4. 心理輔導（精神科專科）<br />\n<br />\n如有需要，請與天水圍逸澤社區主任黃頴思（電話：9547-5825）聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾人平安。<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰"},{"pid":"9f04707b8c410cf0f745826e689840873a2a741c","tid":1412264,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ac04237119494802bb3f938edef6d8164f6b30","tid":1412264,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d7fa29c32dbae12fd0dd33ca54a10f096aa49f","tid":1412264,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfa6bd5625767608d84608cc91e643d35349cf6","tid":1412264,"uid":107060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55009fe68673a37e927959f7ae28975ce832f32","tid":1412264,"uid":35776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:21:20.000Z","msg":"代宣傳<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span styl